</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="280" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,1153,1394]" pageId="5" pageNumber="280">
<bibRefCitation author="Kuwert, A." box="[151,320,1189,1214]" pageId="5" pageNumber="280" pagination="159 - 328" refId="ref5645" refString="Kuwert, A. (1890) Bestimmungs - Tabellen der europaischen Coleopteren. XX Heft. Hydrophilidae. II. Abteilung: Sphaeridiini und Helophorini. Verhandlungen des Naturforschenden Vereins in Brunn, 28 (1889), 159 - 328." type="journal article" year="1890">Kuwert (1890)</bibRefCitation>
mentioned that the distribution of 
<taxonomicName authority="Fairmaire, 1879" authorityName="Fairmaire" authorityYear="1879" box="[732,1197,1189,1214]" class="Insecta" family="Hydraenidae" genus="Ochthebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="280" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="auropallens">
<emphasis box="[732,1003,1189,1213]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="280">Ochthebius auropallens</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Fairmaire, L." box="[1014,1197,1189,1214]" pageId="5" pageNumber="280" pagination="178 - 218" refId="ref4391" refString="Fairmaire, L. (1879) Coleopteres du Nord de l`Afrique. Revue et Magasin de Zoologie Pure et Appliquee, Series 3, 7 (42), 178 - 218." type="journal article" year="1879">Fairmaire, 1879</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
is throughout North Africa including 
<collectingCountry box="[346,417,1226,1250]" name="Egypt" pageId="5" pageNumber="280">Egypt</collectingCountry>
. We have not been able to verify other literature records of this species from 
<collectingCountry box="[1310,1381,1226,1250]" name="Egypt" pageId="5" pageNumber="280">Egypt</collectingCountry>
. The species was not included in the coleopteran lists of 
<bibRefCitation author="Storey, G." box="[737,892,1261,1286]" pageId="5" pageNumber="280" refId="ref6873" refString="Storey, G. (1916) List of Egyptian insects in the collection of the Ministry of Agriculture. No. 5. Technical and Scientific Service (Entomological Section), Government Press, Cairo, 52 pp." type="book" year="1916">Storey (1916)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Alfieri, A." box="[950,1110,1261,1286]" pageId="5" pageNumber="280" pagination="1 - 361" refId="ref3707" refString="Alfieri, A. (1976) Coleoptera of Egypt. Memoires de la Societe entomologique d'Egypt, 5, i - xiii + 1 - 361." type="journal article" year="1976">Alfieri (1976)</bibRefCitation>
. In addition, the species was not included in the revision of 
<bibRefCitation author="Jach, M. A." box="[510,658,1297,1322]" pageId="5" pageNumber="280" pagination="101 - 145" refId="ref4909" refString="Jach, M. A. (1992 b) Revision of the Palearctic species of the genus Ochthebius Leach VI. The marinus group (Hydraenidae, Coleoptera). Entomologica Basiliensia, 14 (1991), 101 - 145." type="journal article" year="1992">Jäch (1992b)</bibRefCitation>
and also not included in the catalogues of 
<bibRefCitation author="Hansen, M." box="[1159,1327,1297,1322]" pageId="5" pageNumber="280" refId="ref4585" refString="Hansen, M. (1998) World catalogue of insects. Vol. 1. Hydraenidae (Coleoptera). Apollo Books, Vester-Skerninge, Denmark, 168 pp." type="book" year="1998">Hansen (1998)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Jach, M. A." pageId="5" pageNumber="280" pagination="102 - 122" refId="ref5214" refString="Jach, M. A. (2004) Hydraenidae. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Smetana, A. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Vol. 2. Apollo Books, Stenstrup, 102 - 122." type="book chapter" year="2004">Jäch (2004)</bibRefCitation>
. The species is known from 
<collectingCountry box="[547,609,1333,1358]" name="Israel" pageId="5" pageNumber="280">Israel</collectingCountry>
and many North African Countries such as 
<collectingCountry box="[1100,1187,1333,1358]" name="Algeria" pageId="5" pageNumber="280">Algeria</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1198,1299,1334,1357]" name="Morocco" pageId="5" pageNumber="280">Morocco</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[1353,1436,1333,1358]" name="Tunisia" pageId="5" pageNumber="280">Tunisia</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Jach, M. A." box="[158,289,1369,1394]" pageId="5" pageNumber="280" pagination="101 - 145" refId="ref4909" refString="Jach, M. A. (1992 b) Revision of the Palearctic species of the genus Ochthebius Leach VI. The marinus group (Hydraenidae, Coleoptera). Entomologica Basiliensia, 14 (1991), 101 - 145." type="journal article" year="1992">Jäch 1992b</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Jach, M. A." box="[301,360,1369,1394]" pageId="5" pageNumber="280" pagination="102 - 122" refId="ref5214" refString="Jach, M. A. (2004) Hydraenidae. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Smetana, A. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Vol. 2. Apollo Books, Stenstrup, 102 - 122." type="book chapter" year="2004">2004</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Hansen, M." box="[372,523,1369,1394]" pageId="5" pageNumber="280" refId="ref4585" refString="Hansen, M. (1998) World catalogue of insects. Vol. 1. Hydraenidae (Coleoptera). Apollo Books, Vester-Skerninge, Denmark, 168 pp." type="book" year="1998">Hansen 1998</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
